## Self-heal contract
When a documented command or runbook step fails during normal work: fix it, update the runbook note in the vault (append the failure + fix to Troubleshooting, bump `verified`), and update the matching `commands.*.verified` date in `.claude/project.json`. When project facts here go stale, update this file too — or run `/project-init` for a full drift report.
